  <heading>BR</heading>
  <desc>
    <brief>
      <para>Branch to Register</para>
    </brief>
    <authored>
      <para>Branch to Register branches unconditionally to an address in a register, with a hint that this is not a subroutine return.</para>
    </authored>
  </desc>
